Package com.currencycloud.coolpay.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadRequestException
    This class implements the exception for bad requests submitted to the server.
    GenericException
    This class implements the exception for requests submitted to the server which returns any other which are not previously implemented, as: - 400 - 401
    UnauthorisedException
    This class implements the exception for unauthorised requests submitted to the server.
